  "keywords": [],
  "notes": [
    "The more zest you add, the more flavor the bread will have. And don't forget to use only the most outer colorful part of the citrus skin.",
    "This recipe works well with other citruses:",
    "* 4–5 limes;",
    "* 3 oranges, 1 lime, cinnamon."
  ],
  "overnight": false,
  "slug": "grapefruit-bread",
  "source": "This recipe is based on [a recipe from Harper’s Bazaar](https://harpersbazaar.com.ua/beauty/diets/gotovim-vmeste-s-harpers-bazaar-rozoviy-greypfrutoviy-keks/).",
  "steps": [
    {
      "name": "",
      "steps": [
        {
          "text": "Preheat oven to 180C.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Grease the baking form with butter.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "In a medium bowl, combine <Ingredient name=\"all-purpose flour\"  />, <Ingredient name=\"baking powder\"  />, and <Ingredient name=\"salt\"  />.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "In a big mixing bowl, combine <Ingredient name=\"butter\"  />, <Ingredient name=\"coconut sugar\"  />, and <Ingredient name=\"date sugar\"  /> using a mixer.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Zest grapefruits into the butter-sugar mix.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Mix in <Ingredient name=\"egg\"  /> into the butter-sugar mix one by one using a mixer.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Add dry ingredients, grapefruit juice (keep about 1/2 grapefruit for the next steps), and milk – little by little of each  – into the wet ingredients mixture, and carefully mix using a silicone spatula.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Pour the batter into the baking form.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Bake for 50-60 minutes.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Once the bread is ready, pour the rest of the grapefruit juice over the bread.",
          "pause": false
        },
        {
          "text": "Let the bread cool down for 10 minutes and remove it from the baking form.",
          "pause": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
